# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Environment Variables for The Digital Archive
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to .env.local (for local dev) or add these
# variables in your hosting dashboard (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)
#
# NEVER commit your actual .env.local file to git.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Your Anthropic API key
# Get one at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Pricing: ~$0.003 per chat message (Claude Sonnet)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
